  <brief_title>A United States Study of the Safety and Tolerability of Corlux for Psychotic Symptoms in Psychotic Major Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel Group Study of the Safety and Efficacy of Three Dose Levels of CORLUXâ„¢ (Mifepristone) Plus an Antidepressant vs. Placebo Plus an Antidepressant in the Treatment of Psychotic Symptoms in Patients With Major Depressive Disorder With Psychotic Features (PMD)</official_title>
